Willie CARROLL, Plaintiff-Appellant/Cross-Appellee,
v.
IOWA DEPARTMENT OF HUMAN SERVICES, Defendant-Appellee/Cross-Appellant. No. 18-0759 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 19, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Willie Carroll appeals, and the Iowa Department of Human Services cross-appeals, a district court ruling on Carroll's petition for judicial review partially affirming an agency determination and remanding the matter to the agency. AFFIRMED ON APPEAL; REVERSED AND REMANDED ON CROSS-APPEAL.

AFFIRMED ON APPEAL; REVERSED AND REMANDED ON CROSS-APPEAL.
